---
title: Fajita-Style Beyond Meat® Bowls with Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, quick and packed with flavour, this dish delivers the fiesta without the fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair beautifully with crispy  Beyond Meat® to create a fajita bowl that comes together with smoky Mexican-style seasoning.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-beyond-meat-style-fajita-26ff7530.jpg
